title.rendered: VIDEO: Lamborghini Huracan Performante Spyder Launch Event

content.rendered:
On the 23rd of August 2018, Prestige Motorcars introduced to the press the newest member of the Huracan family, the Huracan Performante Spyder. Please enjoy our official coverage!
